Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}無論這片廣闊風景向何處延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}RIDE ON THE NEW CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}有時黑白顛倒  也會發生爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}將危機和悲劇統統轉化為堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我們不能夠無功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}即使跌倒了百萬回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}驅散密布的烏雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一定會 OPEN THE WORLDS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}即使我們的終點各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}也要懷抱無數個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}無數次 OPEN THE WORLDS
